---
slug: "testimonials"
permalink: "/es/testimonials/index.html"
title: "Reviews | Morrison Premium Transfer"
description: "Real reviews from Morrison Premium Transfer clients. Only with the author's permission."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Reviews", path: "/es/testimonials/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker">{{ t.testimonialsPage.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1>{{ t.testimonialsPage.title }}</h1>
    <p class="lead">{{ t.testimonialsPage.lead }}</p>
    {% set heroPhoto = { src: "bc-promenade-night", alt: "Paseo marítimo de Balneário Camboriú de noche — puentes e iluminación", ratio: "21-9", modifier: "hero-photo--overlay" } %}
    {% include "partials/hero-photo.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="testimonial-placeholder">
      <p class="statement">{{ t.testimonialsPage.placeholder }}</p>
      <div class="cta-strip-actions" style="margin-top: 1.6rem;">
        <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ t.testimonialsPage.cta }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--bg-soft">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Qué publicamos cuando llega una reseña</h2>
    <ul class="checklist">
      <li>Nombre o iniciales (a elección del autor)</li>
      <li>Ciudad / ruta</li>
      <li>Mes del viaje</li>
      <li>El contenido tal cual, sin editar</li>
      <li>Enlace al perfil (Google, LinkedIn, Instagram) — si el autor lo acepta</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Share your experience?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="mailto:{{ site.contacts.email }}">Email</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
